Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,orang yang paling beruntung!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Luo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Jangan pedulikan aku. Cepat pergi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Cyan...
